title: BRIEF-A2micile Europe H1 net income group share falls to 0.5 mln euros
text:
BRIEF-A2micile Europe H1 net income group share falls to 0.5 mln euros Sept 29 
Sept 29 A2micile Europe SA : 
* Reports H1 net income group share of 0.5 million euros ($562,350.00) compared to 0.7 million euros a year ago 
* H1 EBIT is 1.6 million euros versus 2.0 million euros a year ago 
* H1 total net consolidated income is 1.1 million euros compared to 1.4 million euros a year ago 
* Confirms FY 2017 revenue and profitability target Source text: bit.ly/1KOU68X Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8891 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
